Package org.openid4java.discovery.yadis

Interface Summary
YadisHtmlParser Yadis parser.
 

Class Summary
CyberNekoDOMYadisHtmlParser A YadisHtmlParser implementation using the DOMParser of CyberNeko HTML.
YadisResolver Yadis discovery protocol implementation.
YadisResult The results of Yadis discovery performed on a YadisURL, represented through a stripped-down XRDS model, containing only the those discovery information pieces that are relevant for OpenID.
YadisUrl Wrapper class for various identifiers that are resolvable to URLs and can be used as YadisURLs with the Yadis protocol.
 

Exception Summary
